Visit this link - https://github.com/mjakeman/extension-manager?tab=readme-ov-file
Visit this link - https://flathub.org/apps/com.mattjakeman.ExtensionManager

Run this command - 
1. flatpak install flathub com.mattjakeman.ExtensionManager
2. flatpak run com.mattjakeman.ExtensionManager

Click on Browse and search for "Allow Locked Remote Desktop" and install.
